# GEC.Client (Computer Lock Application)

This application is installed on every client computer (lab PC).

## Main Responsibilities
- Display lock screen until a valid session PIN is entered
- Unlock the PC only for the session duration
- Show session timer (Session Bar)
- Send heartbeat signals to the server database (online detection)
- Automatically lock the screen when time expires

## Security Note
Client computers should not expose admin functions to end-users.
Admin exit is protected using an admin hotkey and credential check.
